Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  快追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快阻止濑乃宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情会按照君岛报告书预言的那样发展的
